Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:11.28,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:26.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:30.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:33.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:36.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:40.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:44.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:48.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:50.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:54.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:59.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:02.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:15.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:18.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,145.389)}The Monstrous Kurage Wolf
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,710.389)}The Rush Hour of Terror
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fusion of man, jellyfish and\Nwolf, Kurage Wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:02:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the product of\Nperfect data assembled
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,by Gel Shocker's incomparable\Nbiologists and computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You will demonstrate your\Npower for our leader at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:26.16,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\c&H192902&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Hayasaka Power Station
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the signal for a drop in voltage...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The voltage... the\Nhigh-voltage current is dropping!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a breakdown somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run some tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- This must be the place.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can escape me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Face my incredible power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He can isolate the current he absorbs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,into positive and negative\Ncharges inside his body,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,letting him unleash a\Npowerful electrical discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,His power would let him drop\Na lightning bolt on Tokyo effortlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a target in\Nmind, General Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have chosen Shinjuku Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.88,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}Shinjuku Station
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Two million people pass through here during\Nthe morning and evening rush hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A properly timed strike\Nwould inspire mass panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader, it is as you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:03.86,Italics,,0,0,0,,General Black, we've\Nspotted a boy at the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good. He might have seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigation team!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look into that boy at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Choco, it's bad for your\Nhealth to eat so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's bad for your skin, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall is the season for food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And they say a person's appetite\Nis the barometer of good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This means I'm the picture of health.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Hongo and Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That means that I don't\Nhave time to goof off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman, what are you\Nin such a hurry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Read a newspaper for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Autumn Night Mystery!\NUnexplained Power Outage."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Two employees of Hayasaka\NPower Station have gone missing."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.64,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs45\c&H192902&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Hayasaka Power Station
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to the police to learn more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A scrap of tattered clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It probably belonged\Nto one of the employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You think the employees were incinerated?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Or electrocuted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at how tattered it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But if they were both struck with a\Nhigh-voltage current, like a lightning bolt,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It very well could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A bunch of monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Policeman, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A bunch of monsters are after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A bunch of monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true! Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where are the monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on... there are no\Nmonsters in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A bunch of monsters are after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Mitsuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,While I do that, you let HQ know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it, Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Mitsuru took his place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I lost 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, better get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's the wrong kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... where did the other one go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk! Talk, or we'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a member of the Rider Kid Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll prove useful. Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now search for the missing whelp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Take Mitsuru to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Take Mitsuru and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... how do you like\Nthe feel of a 100,000 volt shock?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your mind, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no ordinary man... I'm a cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it... it does work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance to kill you! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Knee Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurage Wolf...\Nwe'll finish this another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... he got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:45.87,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mr. Hongo!\N- What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Taki and Mitsuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to Shinjuku Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinjuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to meet a friend.\NMr. Nakamura, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,An old friend from his racing\Ndays, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:10.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an7}Shinjuku Station
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:17.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nakamura arriving on Alps Flight 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nakamura. You have a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:23.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nakamura. Mr. Nakamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a call. Could\Nyou wait here a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I'll bring the car around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, over here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the call about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Mistaken identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Get in, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that strange shock?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't turned the key,\Nbut the engine's already on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have to take\Nit in for a check up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't find Mr. Taki or Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He and Mitsuru are still out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowhere serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to make an introduction:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my best friend, Nakamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Rider Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd that electric charge come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:39.69,Italics,,0,0,0,,I can hear an electric current...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As a cyborg, Hongo Takeshi's ears\Nare many times more powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:44.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,than those of a normal human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:46.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's coming from Nakamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look into this, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakamura, let's go on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's swap some stories from the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll take your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are you doing?!\N- Pops, he's a Gel Shocker monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,His touch is deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be electrocuted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your end has come at last, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone... run away, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one obstacle out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki! Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki and the child are\Nalready in our custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you've interfered with us so often,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll execute Operation: Detonate Shinjuku\NStation right in front of your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't make lightning that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you don't know the\Nprinciple behind lightning strikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Any child knows that positive\Nand negative currents collide in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to make them happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My body can isolate positive\Nand negative electric currents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, my right arm is positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The left arm is negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:44.93,Italics,,0,0,0,,You expect it to be that easy, Kurage Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice... the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:55.86,Italics,,0,0,0,,I see... so you can only use your power\Nif your arms can come together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! I saw you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:18:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You underestimated me, Kurage Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy for me to feign death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you... this isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki. See to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have spotted his weak point,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still have a hard fight ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Persistent fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, feel the extent of my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:23.56,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:27.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:31.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:34.56,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:38.12,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:41.75,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.31,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:47.91,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:52.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:56.12,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:06.81,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:10.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:13.86,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:17.55,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:21.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:25.15,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.48,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:31.01,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:35.53,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:39.02,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:50.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:53.19,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:57.33,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:22:00.61,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:04.34,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:07.75,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:11.18,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:14.53,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:18.84,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:22.09,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, and he dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have enough\Npower to kill one person!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nakamura! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Drill Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.36,0:22:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.41,0:22:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nakamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I took them to HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And the boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.84,0:22:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Toru?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was going to join\Nthe Kamen Rider Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:22:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:03.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider fought desperately\Nto see Kurage Wolf's hideous plan foiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.34,0:23:06.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Gel Shocker was already\Npreparing their next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:07.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight on, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:10.63,Cont,,0,65,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(300.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:14.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Servant of my beloved Geldam...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:18.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let us celebrate the birth\Nof a new power, Inokabuton.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.63,0:23:21.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now, awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:24.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Throw Kamen Rider to the pits of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:27.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:30.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,we'll meet again next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:30.84,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fs115\bord0.9\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,710.389)}Monstrous Inokabuton, \NDefeat Kamen Rider With Insanity Gas
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:50.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:57.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:24:01.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:05.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:08.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.90,0:24:12.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Kurage Wolf\NThe Rush Hour of Terror